programme.title: Alexander
programme.desc: The young Macedonian king (Colin Farrell) and general leads his army into battle to conquer much of the known world.

programme.title: The Purge: Election Year
programme.desc: Former Police Sergeant Barnes becomes head of security for Senator Charlie Roan, a Presidential candidate targeted for death on Purge night due to her vow to eliminate the Purge.

programme.title: Atomic Blonde
programme.desc: With the Berlin Wall about to fall, an elite MI6 spy travels into the heart of the city to retrieve a priceless dossier and take down a ruthless espionage ring.

programme.title: Baby Driver
programme.desc: Coerced into working for a crime boss, a talented getaway driver must face the music when a doomed heist threatens his life, love and freedom.

programme.title: Now You See Me
programme.desc: A federal agent (Mark Ruffalo) and an Interpol detective (Melanie Laurent) play a cat-and-mouse game with cunning illusionists who rob corrupt business leaders during their performances, then funnel the money to members of the audience.

programme.title: Blood Money
programme.desc: Three friends on a wilderness excursion find a fortune stashed in the woods. Now they must outrun the white collar criminal who is hell bent on retrieving his money.

programme.title: Wrath of the Titans
